    "Participants were then matched with either another participant (human partner condition) or GPT-EXPLORING HUMAN AND AI EMOTIONAL SUPPORT 4 (AI partner condition).",
    "Participants were not aware of the identity of their partner.",
    "They were then asked to share a negative experience they recently had: \"Please write about a recent negative social experience.",
    "This could be a minor or major event, in any area of your life, and could involve family, friends, or others.\"",
    "Participants both shared a negative experience and received one from their counterpart, which was either AI or human."
